Package com.collabnet.ce.soap60.webservices.discussion

Class PostSoapRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.collabnet.ce.soap60.webservices.discussion.PostSoapRow
  • public class PostSoapRow
extends Object
    A discussion post list is represented by PostSoapList. Each row within a post list is represented by the PostSoapRow class.
